name: Abstract 002
description: Hello. My name is Quest! I am 2 years old with high functioning autism. This is one of my abstract paintings produced on procreate. I created this all on my own with no help at all.  I hope you find as much joy in my art as I have creating it. Collecting my work helps my parents make sure I get the support that I need and save for my future. I hope you like it and there's more to come!!
